WEBVTT

00:00:01.501 --> 00:00:03.136 line:90%
Jony Ive: For
more than a decade,

00:00:03.136 --> 00:00:08.642 line:90%
our intention has been to create
an iPhone that is all display.

00:00:08.642 --> 00:00:12.579 line:90%
A physical object that
disappears into the experience.

00:00:12.579 --> 00:00:16.049 line:90%
♪ Music playing ♪

00:00:16.049 --> 00:00:17.784 line:90%
This is iPhone X.

00:00:17.784 --> 00:00:20.520 align:middle line:10% position:90% size:3%
♪

00:00:20.520 --> 00:00:22.990 line:90%
Developing the form
and display together

00:00:22.990 --> 00:00:26.026 line:90%
defines a whole new integration,

00:00:26.026 --> 00:00:28.929 line:90%
making the boundary between
the device and the screen

00:00:28.929 --> 00:00:31.398 line:90%
hard to discern.

00:00:31.398 --> 00:00:34.701 line:90%
The custom OLED panel
was engineered to fold

00:00:34.701 --> 00:00:39.072 line:90%
and seamlessly combine with
the external surfaces.

00:00:39.072 --> 00:00:43.110 line:90%
Mechanical buttons give way
to touch and gestures.

00:00:43.110 --> 00:00:44.845 line:90%
There's no Home button.

00:00:44.845 --> 00:00:48.415 line:90%
A single swipe takes you
to the Home screen.

00:00:48.415 --> 00:00:53.086 line:90%
A more responsive touch system
means the gestures in iOS 11

00:00:53.086 --> 00:00:54.221 line:90%
are more fluid.

00:00:54.221 --> 00:00:56.556 align:middle line:10% position:90% size:3%
♪

00:00:56.556 --> 00:00:58.792 line:90%
The polished
stainless steel band

00:00:58.792 --> 00:01:03.363 line:90%
reinforces the water-resistant,
all glass design.

00:01:03.363 --> 00:01:05.032 line:90%
This new glass formulation,

00:01:05.032 --> 00:01:07.634 line:90%
the most durable ever
in a smartphone,

00:01:07.634 --> 00:01:11.405 line:90%
enables, for the first time,
wireless charging.

00:01:13.206 --> 00:01:15.442 line:90%
Our new TrueDepth camera system,

00:01:15.442 --> 00:01:17.978 line:90%
contained within
this tiny space,

00:01:17.978 --> 00:01:21.481 line:90%
uses extraordinary
depth sensing technology

00:01:21.481 --> 00:01:24.484 line:90%
to let you unlock your phone
with a glance.

00:01:24.484 --> 00:01:26.520 align:middle line:10% position:90% size:3%
♪

00:01:26.520 --> 00:01:29.389 line:90%
We call this FaceID.

00:01:29.389 --> 00:01:31.992 line:90%
It maps the unique
geometry of your face

00:01:31.992 --> 00:01:37.164 line:90%
with over 30,000 invisible dots.

00:01:37.164 --> 00:01:40.133 line:90%
This data is analyzed
by the neural engine

00:01:40.133 --> 00:01:45.105 line:90%
on the A11 bionic chip,
the first of its kind.

00:01:45.105 --> 00:01:48.308 line:90%
Your iPhone now
recognizes you,

00:01:48.308 --> 00:01:53.747 line:90%
even in the dark, and will
adapt to your physical changes.

00:01:53.747 --> 00:01:57.384 line:90%
This makes your face
your secure password.

00:01:57.384 --> 00:01:58.819 line:90%
So with just a look,

00:01:58.819 --> 00:02:03.690 line:90%
you can authenticate your phone
or use Apple Pay.

00:02:03.690 --> 00:02:08.762 line:90%
The TrueDepth camera also
enables new experiences.

00:02:08.762 --> 00:02:10.897 line:90%
Like bringing emojis to life

00:02:10.897 --> 00:02:15.135 line:90%
by mapping more than 50
facial muscles in real time.

00:02:15.135 --> 00:02:17.204 line:90%
So you can be happy,

00:02:17.204 --> 00:02:18.839 line:90%
or sad,

00:02:18.839 --> 00:02:19.840 line:90%
or cross.

00:02:19.840 --> 00:02:23.276 align:middle line:10% position:90% size:3%
♪

00:02:23.276 --> 00:02:25.946 line:90%
Both the front-
and rear-facing cameras

00:02:25.946 --> 00:02:27.714 line:90%
now have Portrait Mode.

00:02:27.714 --> 00:02:28.749 line:90%
And for the first time,

00:02:28.749 --> 00:02:33.153 line:90%
you can actually
define the light in a scene.

00:02:33.153 --> 00:02:36.757 line:90%
Based on fundamental
photographic principles,

00:02:36.757 --> 00:02:38.091 line:10%
Portrait lighting

00:02:38.091 --> 00:02:43.330 line:10%
produces the effect
of real studio lighting.

00:02:43.330 --> 00:02:44.064 line:90%
On the back,

00:02:44.064 --> 00:02:48.001 line:90%
the dual camera system
is completely redesigned.

00:02:48.001 --> 00:02:52.906 line:90%
It's made even smarter
by the A11 bionic chip.

00:02:52.906 --> 00:02:54.274 line:90%
With machine learning,

00:02:54.274 --> 00:02:56.543 line:90%
the camera detects
elements in the scene

00:02:56.543 --> 00:03:02.516 line:90%
to optimize the image
before the photo is even taken.

00:03:02.516 --> 00:03:08.755 line:90%
The camera we use every day
now delivers so much more.

00:03:08.755 --> 00:03:09.890 line:90%
And as iOS becomes

00:03:09.890 --> 00:03:13.827 line:90%
the world's largest platform
for augmented reality,

00:03:13.827 --> 00:03:16.129 line:90%
it will redefine
what's possible.

00:03:16.129 --> 00:03:20.100 align:middle line:10% position:90% size:3%
♪

00:03:20.100 --> 00:03:22.736 line:90%
This is iPhone X.

00:03:22.736 --> 00:03:25.138 align:middle line:10% position:90% size:3%
♪
